{"tid":154324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國國民黨智庫陳鵬仁:美駐軍台灣視同侵略中國","createTime":"2017-03-13T08:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T10:10:35.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb24fcc6156a55adfa13b5a2b6e7863ca98e146","tid":154324,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:22:37.000Z","msg":"台美中/陳鵬仁:美駐軍台灣視同侵略中國大陸<br />\n<br />\n中國國民黨智庫、國家政策研究基金會資深顧問、文化大學日文系特約講座教授陳鵬仁接受中評社訪問時表示，美國與日本雖然&ldquo;同盟&rdquo;，其實是美國想讓中國大陸知道&ldquo;打狗要看主人&rdquo;，同時也告訴日本，若是主動挑釁美國也保不了日本。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">外傳美國有意派駐軍隊、甚至是&ldquo;薩德&rdquo;飛彈防禦系統進駐台灣。陳鵬仁表示，日本安倍政府仍支持美軍駐紮在琉球；其次美國也不敢，因為這等於公然與中共為敵，中共可以控訴美國侵佔台灣視同侵略中國</span></span>。蔡英文知道這麼做只會增加台灣的危險而已，相信她也不敢。中共只要封鎖台灣海峽，對所有商船、運輸船安檢、嚴禁台商或外資的錢從大陸匯到台灣，幾個月台灣就垮了。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　陳鵬仁對中評社表示，很多人講日本首相安倍晉三是日本的右派份子，因為他的外祖父、前日本首相岸信介也是偏向國家主義意識形態的右派；安倍緊拉著美國總統特朗普，其實知道美國不可能為了日本的安危，和擁有核武的中共發生衝突，所以安倍只是做給日本人看、讓日本人相信日本的保鑣、美國老闆愛護日本，好鞏固安倍的政權，並希望下次選舉能再勝選繼續執政；這是安倍一種心理戰。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　他指出，有人質疑安倍有意讓日本重新走上軍國主義道路，國際情勢、環境和過去已經完全不一樣。而且日本不得以軍事武力去解決國際爭端清楚的寫在日本的&ldquo;和平&ldquo;憲法&rdquo;裡，日本應該不會再次走向軍國主義。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　他分析，美日同盟就美國而言，只是給日本吃一顆定心丸，美國只想讓中共知道&ldquo;這條狗的主人是美國的，牠沒咬人、頂多只會叫叫，不能隨便打牠，如果打牠視同打美國&rdquo;。同樣的，美國也會告訴日本，中共的軍艦、飛機到釣魚台海域航行、頂多只是繞繞，不會逗留太久，沒必要主動挑釁，如果日本主動挑釁，美國也保不了日本。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　他說，不論是美國、俄羅斯、中國，彼此或許可能發生小磨擦，但不可能會有正面衝突。以前戰爭是有限度的戰爭，造成的傷害不是那麼大，但1945年美國在日本廣島投下原子彈，到現在一顆氫彈的威力更勝過去幾百倍，假如真的開戰，人類一定會滅亡，沒有誰贏誰輸的問題。這些先進科技大國應該都有認知，一旦正面衝突，恐怕會是互相毁滅，沒有誰贏誰輸的問題。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　蔡英文一直爭取美日保台。陳鵬仁對中評社表示，國際政治上，任何作為都可能影響深遠，所以任何作為一定要想到後果。蔡英文團隊只想拉美日就是沒有思考可能衍生的後果；包括近日&ldquo;去蔣&rdquo;、&ldquo;去中國化&rdquo;、&ldquo;批孔&rdquo;等作為都在製造兩岸不必要的緊張。如果中共對台灣動武，美國要怎麼幫忙？頂多派駐紮在琉球的美軍馳援，但中共不論要對台採取何種軍事作為，一定會先試探、推演、評估美國會干預到什麼程度。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n　他分析，台灣對美國而言不是那麼重要，川普政府的政策走向要等執政4個月後才會逐漸明朗，但以商人講利益的性格來說，台灣某種程度上是美國的燙手山芋，頂多當棋子和中共討價還價，只要這棋子不合用，就有可能&ldquo;賣給&rdquo;大陸；例如川普廢掉TPP，就是想用各個擊破的方式讓美國利益極大化。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cdnews.com.tw/cdnews_site/docDetail.jsp?coluid=141&amp;docid=104076703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdnews.com.tw%2Fcdnews_site%2FdocDetail.jsp%3Fcoluid%3D141%26docid%3D104076703&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=30732f4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cdnews.com.tw/cdnews_site/docDetail.jsp?coluid=141&amp;docid=104076703</a>"},{"pid":"9102689d4e3bebcdbdd9a6f90f415d0ef0734b3c","tid":154324,"uid":521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"地球是中國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db70bcbb40d0ab4cf0f41040196ab0cdc1354bb","tid":154324,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記兩蔣年代<br />\n由韓戰至1978年<br />\n美國曾在台灣駐軍<br />\n最多時有20萬人"},{"pid":"afa374956bcd6795a60f2eedf8916160c160b8e1","tid":154324,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"一直都有駐軍啦"},{"pid":"17d8df243848b21750b453c64a3d287ce42d5f68","tid":154324,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1ad4157fbe2f5af1a90a274428c500d2d17e80","tid":154324,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"好彩太陽花運動<br />\n服貿沒有通過<br />\n否則已變成中國台灣特區"},{"pid":"a1d562160cef414608bf945ce90c3c94851c47fb","tid":154324,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"成部雷達係美軍管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會無駐軍"},{"pid":"585a77b52e55ca8138e90c3c2cbf20399a49d6ff","tid":154324,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:29:43.000Z","msg":"國民黨人到底知不知道共產黨的禍害！"},{"pid":"ab1784e2f65c9197797effaeaa3df7388179def1","tid":154324,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家係台灣既民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4576b54d1ce3c8e72e18ba683536e25fabf5f08","tid":154324,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家係台灣既民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n國共本源自孫中山聯俄容共黃埔軍校"},{"pid":"3e7a8e9db194bcb72bfca886471128f4795b5119","tid":154324,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國民黨人到底知不知道共產黨的禍害！</blockquote><br />\n你知唔知國民黨別名係支那共產黨台灣分部"},{"pid":"1f8448ed6f5914b2edaa10940211dd72e52af2fe","tid":154324,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"美國人係靠不斷打仗來維持軍費開支，世界上邊個地方有仗打就會有美軍身影。全世界最大嘅軍備出口國已經維持70年，今日唔係話大陸打唔贏台灣，而事實係大陸攻入台灣之後美國會唔會係「台灣關係法」名義底下派兩個航母群炸鳩你成個島，最後成個台灣收埋，二戰當年美軍照樣炸到台北高雄反轉哂。而美國嘅外交政策係唔會因為邊個總統上台而會有重大改變，<br />\n韓國今日變成咁就有板俾大家睇。"},{"pid":"7f282f767a773e74744ace3747d52dd8bdb7c611","tid":154324,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:47:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家係台灣既民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好似人大都有國民黨代表<br />\n用黎坐"},{"pid":"05d4f41203b95ed68fe5bc301e785773ce4c4933","tid":154324,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"國民黨同共產黨合併未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99423f7b3593cc2d763c49dfafff4c033abc8959","tid":154324,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"當年國民黨為左美國駐軍協防就快連幫艾森豪bj都肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ad/%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E8%89%BE%E6%A3%AE%E8%B1%AA_TAIWAN_welcomes_U.S._President_Eisenhower_in_1960.jpg/210px-%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E8%89%BE%E6%A3%AE%E8%B1%AA_TAIWAN_welcomes_U.S._President_Eisenhower_in_1960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fa%2Fad%2F%25E8%2587%25BA%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E8%2589%25BE%25E6%25A3%25AE%25E8%25B1%25AA_TAIWAN_welcomes_U.S._President_Eisenhower_in_1960.jpg%2F210px-%25E8%2587%25BA%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E8%2589%25BE%25E6%25A3%25AE%25E8%25B1%25AA_TAIWAN_welcomes_U.S._President_Eisenhower_in_1960.jpg&h=e83b5d6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4070135762aacabb8b0b720c69ad1609336098db","tid":154324,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"根據舊金山和約<br />\n台澎主權未定<br />\n<br />\n如果美軍駐軍福建省金門和馬祖<br />\n侵略中國就成立"},{"pid":"a0150fb2804fa135d6e6262a7334d69baaedcfe4","tid":154324,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"中國國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我笑撚到收唔到聲"}]}